data.description:
2310 Pleasant Ridge Road Rogers, Arkansas 72756 - 169,900

Beautiful 4 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage home on over an acre of land! 2217 SQFT, 2 Living Areas, 2 bedrooms with walk in closets. 9 ft ceilings, Fireplace, Dining room and eat-in kitchen. This is really a beautiful property. Close to gas stations, food, market and is located in the beautiful countryside of Northwest Arkansas. Out of city limits. Fully remodeled, new granite counterspies in kitchen, both bathrooms, desk area. Redone with gorgeous oil rubbed bronze finish. Good size shed with new paint. Fire Pit in the back yard. Back fenced in patio. Landscape stone and mulch. Hardwired smoke alarms will help keep you and your family safe. Extra electrical outlets. Large lot. City water, trash, Electric, Gas, Cable hook up. Washer and dryer connect. Great Furnace, A/C Unit, Hot water heater and Roof. 1.07 Acres m/l. All new set of matching stainless steel appliances. 

Brand New:
-Granite Countertops
-Stainless Steel Appliances
(Gas Range, Microwave, Dishwasher)
-Paint
-Light Fixtures and Fans
-Door Hardware and knobs
-Carpet
-Tile
-Sinks
-Faucets
-Shower Door
-Shower Hardware 
-Fire Pit
-Garage Door
-Blinds
-Hardwired Smoke Alarms
-Mirrored Closet Doors
-Landscape Stone and Mulch 

Owner-agent. If buyer works with me and no buyers agent fee is paid I will have a lot more room to work on the price. 

Please call or text with any questions or to set up a personal showing today. 

Chadwick Clay
479-640-1472
Aladdin Realtors
